Town Square is intended as an interactive resource for our readers. Policy Review welcomes suggestions for publications, events, and news for inclusion. Contact: <i>Policy Review</i>, 214 Massachusetts Ave., N.E. Washington, D.C. 20002. Tel: 202-546-4400 Fax: 202-608-6136. E-mail: polrev@heritage.org
