http://www.atr.org:80/townhall/spotlights/9-11-95/bennalex.html 204.71.237.87 19970210023155 text/html 23135
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 10-Feb-97 02:32:41 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 20-Oct-95 14:26:45 GMT
