http://www.atr.org:80/empower/ct-11155.html 204.71.237.87 19970209094527 text/html 13337
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 09:46:08 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 02-Jul-96 20:54:55 GMT
Content-length: 13152
Content-type: text/html
