http://www.atr.org:80/empower/new/opinion.htm 204.71.237.87 19970210024522 text/html 5196
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 10-Feb-97 02:46:07 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 26-Jul-96 13:40:29 GMT
Content-length: 5013
