http://www.atr.org:80/empower/ps-afirm.html 204.71.237.87 19970210032233 text/html 8925
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 10-Feb-97 03:23:18 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 02-Jul-96 20:54:53 GMT
